This paper focuses on graph signal processing, specifically on spectral filters on graphs. The paper discusses the transferability of filters from one graph to another, which is important in graph convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GR (Graphics), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
